1
00:01:30,150 --> 00:01:31,110
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="40"><font color="#2d1508">Hell's Paradise</font></font></b></font>

2
00:01:31,110 --> 00:01:36,470
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>A faint flower was blooming 
unnoticed by anyone</b></font>

3
00:01:36,470 --> 00:01:41,470
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Not a burning red, 
but flickering serenely in red</b></font>

4
00:01:41,470 --> 00:01:46,820
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I've been pausing for a long time 
dragging my past at my feet</b></font>

5
00:01:46,820 --> 00:01:49,420
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>If I break free from this ambivalence,</b></font>

6
00:01:49,420 --> 00:01:52,830
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>will I be able to bloom by its side?</b></font>

7
00:01:52,830 --> 00:01:55,470
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>The future is slipping away 
between my fingers</b></font>

8
00:01:55,470 --> 00:01:57,990
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>What mistake did I make 
to pay this price?</b></font>

9
00:01:57,990 --> 00:02:02,840
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Always hurting myself</b></font>

10
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:08,190
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>and hesitant even to a small joy</b></font>

11
00:02:08,700 --> 00:02:10,390
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I want to stop now</b></font>

12
00:02:10,390 --> 00:02:12,910
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>The flower just bloomed in dignity</b></font>

13
00:02:12,910 --> 00:02:15,530
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>and that was all I needed to be happy</b></font>

14
00:02:15,530 --> 00:02:20,300
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I just wanted to protect this one flower</b></font>

15
00:02:20,650 --> 00:02:23,360
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Wishing to be strong, I</b></font>

16
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:26,020
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>picked up the vulnerability 
I had once cast away</b></font>

17
00:02:26,020 --> 00:02:27,970
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Can't break free from the ambivalence</b></font>

18
00:02:27,970 --> 00:02:31,160
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>In ambivalence, I become myself</b></font>

19
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:33,870
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Like rooting strongly into the soil</b></font>

20
00:02:33,870 --> 00:02:36,420
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>like swaying ephemerally to the wind</b></font>

21
00:02:36,420 --> 00:02:39,650
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I'm slowly loosening myself to bloom</b></font>

22
00:02:39,510 --> 00:02:42,720
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="40">Hell's Paradise</font></b></font>

23
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:52,530
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>Chrysanthemum and Peach</b></font>

24
00:04:32,170 --> 00:04:36,170
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b></b>{\an8}<font color="#555557"><font size="25">Sakataya Rice</font></font></font>

25
00:05:57,460 --> 00:06:05,720
{\an8}<font color="#e4f0dd">Wood</font>

26
00:05:57,460 --> 00:06:05,720
{\an8}<font color="#e6acaf">Fire</font>

27
00:05:57,460 --> 00:06:05,720
{\an8}<font color="#f3e0d4">Earth</font>

28
00:05:57,460 --> 00:06:05,720
{\an8}<font color="#e5dec7">Metal</font>

29
00:05:57,460 --> 00:06:05,720
{\an8}<font color="#dce9f5">Water</font>

30
00:09:07,270 --> 00:09:11,020
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#03020f"><font size="25">Hell's Paradise</font></font></b></font>

31
00:19:00,580 --> 00:19:05,920
{\an8}<font color="#e4f0dd">Wood</font>

32
00:19:00,580 --> 00:19:05,920
{\an8}<font color="#e6acaf">Fire</font>

33
00:19:00,580 --> 00:19:05,920
{\an8}<font color="#f3e0d4">Earth</font>

34
00:19:00,580 --> 00:19:05,920
{\an8}<font color="#e5dec7">Metal</font>

35
00:19:00,580 --> 00:19:05,920
{\an8}<font color="#dce9f5">Water</font>

36
00:21:08,100 --> 00:21:14,230
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>On the other side, even today</b></font>

37
00:21:14,230 --> 00:21:20,190
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Someone is unraveling, 
yet they still stand</b></font>

38
00:21:20,190 --> 00:21:26,100
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>A stab to the chest, this loneliness</b></font>

39
00:21:26,100 --> 00:21:31,930
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Points and lines, 
breaking off and vanishing</b></font>

40
00:21:31,930 --> 00:21:34,830
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>My shattered mask</b></font>

41
00:21:34,830 --> 00:21:37,910
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>It's more than I can bear</b></font>

42
00:21:37,910 --> 00:21:40,900
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>But I must keep on living</b></font>

43
00:21:40,900 --> 00:21:45,690
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Tomorrow awaits to greet me</b></font>

44
00:21:45,690 --> 00:21:48,650
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>It's endless</b></font>

45
00:21:48,650 --> 00:21:51,220
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>And so fragile</b></font>

46
00:21:51,220 --> 00:21:57,450
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Is it better to believe 
hearts don't exist at all?</b></font>

47
00:21:57,450 --> 00:22:03,010
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Radiant and soft</b></font>

48
00:22:03,010 --> 00:22:04,720
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Was the hand</b></font>

49
00:22:04,720 --> 00:22:13,300
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I squeezed back on that day</b></font>

